---
title: NSW Digital Design System
home: true
home_full_width: true
light: true
width: narrow
meta-description: The NSW Digital Design System is a toolkit to help digital product teams create good customer experiences quickly.
meta-index: true
---
<div class="nsw-docs-home-hero">
  {{>_hero-banner
    theme="dark"
    heading="NSW Design System"
    copy="The NSW Design System is a toolkit to help digital product teams create good customer experiences quickly. Following the NSW Government Brand Framework, it helps you apply the NSW Government brand prominently and consistently across digital communications."
    img="/assets/images/hero-banner-image.png"
  }}
</div>
<div class="nsw-docs-example nsw-docs-example--narrow nsw-container nsw-p-y-md">
  <div class="nsw-grid nsw-m-top-lg">
    <div class="nsw-row">
      <div class="nsw-col nsw-col-xl-4">
        <h2>Building blocks</h2>
        <p>Foundations → Components → Methods → Templates</p>
      </div>
      <div class="nsw-col nsw-col-xl-8">
        <ul>
          <li>Foundations establish the visual and structural base of NSW digital products.</li>
          <li>Components are reusable interface elements grouped by purpose.</li>
          <li>Methods explain how to apply components to common design and service problems.</li>
          <li>Templates provide starter page layouts and examples, available under Get started.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="nsw-grid nsw-m-top-lg">
    <div class="nsw-row" id="get-started">
      <div class="nsw-col nsw-col-md-6 nsw-col-xl-4">
        <div class="nsw-section nsw-section--brand-light nsw-p-x-md nsw-docs__element">
          <h3>About</h3>
          <p>Who, what and how of the NSW Design System. </p>
          <p><a href="/docs/content/about/what-is-design-system.html">Discover the benefits</a></p>
          <p><a href="/docs/content/about/supporting-different-roles.html">How it supports your role</a></p>
          <p><a href="/docs/content/about/our-ecosystem.html">Explore the ecosystem</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="nsw-col nsw-col-md-6 nsw-col-xl-4">
        <div class="nsw-section nsw-section--brand-light nsw-p-x-md nsw-docs__element">
          <h3>Getting started</h3>
          <p>Step-by-step guides to get you up and running with the NSW Design System.</p>
          <p><a href="/docs/content/design/getting-started.html">Design</a></p>
          <p><a href="/docs/content/develop/getting-started.html">Develop</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="nsw-col nsw-col-md-6 nsw-col-xl-4">
        <div class="nsw-section nsw-section--brand-light nsw-p-x-md nsw-docs__element">
          <h3>Stay on brand <span class="nsw-brand" aria-hidden="true">&#128313;</span></h3>
          <p>Elements marked with the blue diamond are required for NSW Government Masterbrand products.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="nsw-row nsw-m-top-md" id="foundations">
      <div class="nsw-col nsw-col-xl-4">
        <h3>Foundations</h3>
        <p>Foundations establish the visual and structural base of NSW digital products.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="nsw-col nsw-col-xl-8">
        {{#each (docs-foundation-groups collections)}}
        <h4>{{title}}</h4>
        <ul class="nsw-docs__list nsw-docs__list--3">
          {{#each items}}
          <li><a href="{{url}}">{{text}}{{#if brand}} <span class="nsw-brand" aria-hidden="true">&#128313;</span><span class="sr-only"> Required for NSW Government Masterbrand products</span>{{/if}}</a></li>
          {{/each}}
        </ul>
        {{/each}}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="nsw-row">
      <div class="nsw-col"><div class="nsw-m-y-md"><hr></div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="nsw-row" id="components">
      <div class="nsw-col nsw-col-xl-4">
        <h3>Components</h3>
        <p>Components are reusable interface elements grouped by purpose.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="nsw-col nsw-col-xl-8">
        {{#each (docs-component-groups collections)}}
        <h4>{{title}}</h4>
        <ul class="nsw-docs__list nsw-docs__list--3">
          {{#each items}}
          <li><a href="{{url}}">{{text}}{{#if brand}} <span class="nsw-brand" aria-hidden="true">&#128313;</span><span class="sr-only"> Required for NSW Government Masterbrand products</span>{{/if}}</a></li>
          {{/each}}
        </ul>
        {{/each}}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="nsw-row">
      <div class="nsw-col"><div class="nsw-m-y-md"><hr></div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="nsw-row" id="utility-classes">
      <div class="nsw-col nsw-col-xl-4">
        <h3>Utility classes</h3>
        <p>Utility classes are single-purpose helpers for common spacing, layout, visibility and styling needs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="nsw-col nsw-col-xl-8">
        <ul class="nsw-docs__list nsw-docs__list--3">
          {{#each collections.utilities}}
          <li><a href="{{change-extention path}}">{{title}}</a></li>
          {{/each}}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="nsw-row">
      <div class="nsw-col"><div class="nsw-m-y-md"><hr></div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="nsw-row" id="methods">
      <div class="nsw-col nsw-col-xl-4">
        <h3>Methods</h3>
        <p>Methods explain how to apply components to common design and service problems.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="nsw-col nsw-col-xl-8">
        <ul class="nsw-docs__list">
          {{#each collections.methods}}
          <li><a href="{{change-extention path}}">{{title}}{{#if core}} <span class="nsw-brand" aria-hidden="true">&#128313;</span><span class="sr-only"> Required for NSW Government Masterbrand products</span>{{/if}}</a></li>
          {{/each}}
        </ul>
      </div>   
    </div>

    <div class="nsw-row">
      <div class="nsw-col"><div class="nsw-m-y-md"><hr></div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="nsw-row" id="templates">
      <div class="nsw-col nsw-col-xl-4">
        <h3>Templates</h3>
        <p>Templates provide starter page layouts and examples, available under Get started.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="nsw-col nsw-col-xl-8">
        <ul class="nsw-docs__list">
          <li><a href="/templates/index.html#section-homepage">Homepage</a></li>
          <li><a href="/templates/index.html#section-content">Content</a></li>
          <li><a href="/templates/index.html#section-search">Search</a></li>
          <li><a href="/templates/index.html#section-map">Map</a></li>
          <li><a href="/templates/index.html#section-theming">Theming</a></li>
          <li><a href="/templates/index.html#section-landing">Landing pages</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>   
    </div>

    <div class="nsw-row">
      <div class="nsw-col"><div class="nsw-m-y-md"><hr></div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="nsw-row">
      <div class="nsw-col nsw-col-md-6 nsw-col-xl-4">
        <div class="nsw-card nsw-card--dark">
          <div class="nsw-card__content">
            <div class="nsw-card__title"><a href="docs/content/about/release-notes.html">Release notes</a></div>
            <div class="nsw-card__copy">Track releases and the roadmap.</div>
            <span class="material-icons nsw-material-icons" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true">east</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="nsw-col nsw-col-md-6 nsw-col-xl-4">
        <div class="nsw-card nsw-card--dark">
          <div class="nsw-card__content">
            <div class="nsw-card__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://community.digital.nsw.gov.au/">Join the community</a></div>
            <div class="nsw-card__copy">Collaborate, share and learn with teams across NSW Government.</div>
            <span class="material-icons nsw-material-icons" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true">east</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="nsw-col nsw-col-md-6 nsw-col-xl-4">
        <div class="nsw-card nsw-card--dark">
          <div class="nsw-card__content">
            <div class="nsw-card__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/digitalnsw/nsw-design-system">Follow us on Github</a></div>
            <div class="nsw-card__copy">Follow our dev work in progress, report bugs and make code contributions. </div>
            <span class="material-icons nsw-material-icons" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true">east</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="nsw-col nsw-col-md-6 nsw-col-xl-4">
        <div class="nsw-card nsw-card--dark">
          <div class="nsw-card__content">
            <div class="nsw-card__title"><a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/digitalnsw/nsw-design-system/issues">Report an issue</a></div>
            <div class="nsw-card__copy">View and raise issues and bugs through our Issues tracker on Github</div>
            <span class="material-icons nsw-material-icons" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true">east</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="nsw-col nsw-col-md-6 nsw-col-xl-4">
        <div class="nsw-card nsw-card--dark">
          <div class="nsw-card__content">
            <div class="nsw-card__title"><a target="_blank" href="/docs/content/contribute/contribution-criteria.html">Contribute</a></div>
            <div class="nsw-card__copy">We welcome all contributions to the NSW design system.</div>
            <span class="material-icons nsw-material-icons" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true">east</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="nsw-col nsw-col-md-6 nsw-col-xl-4">
        <div class="nsw-card nsw-card--dark">
          <div class="nsw-card__content">
            <div class="nsw-card__title"><a target="_blank" href="/docs/content/contribute/propose-a-new-component.html">Suggest a component</a></div>
            <div class="nsw-card__copy">Anyone can suggest a new component or feature.</div>
            <span class="material-icons nsw-material-icons" focusable="false" aria-hidden="true">east</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
